{"tid":136531,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人仲記得不能說的秘密?","createTime":"2017-02-27T06:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T18:19:23.000Z","uid":11581,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"04476729b0213148c017591e4fae963cd5fcfd04","tid":136531,"uid":11581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T06:22:49.000Z","msg":"想當年對呢套戲大跌眼鏡...睇預告個陣諗住係周杰倫自HIGH既電影<br />\n(心諗彈琴 彈到棟樓爛晒係咩Q野事...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n後尾DOWN左落黎睇先覺得正 以後搵女朋友都要路小雨咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD配樂更加唔洗講 得閒做野都會播住係到聽 真係好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而個結局係正既(以下劇透 唔想俾人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n(我見好似幾多人唔明下就解釋下, 周杰倫最後彈得太快番去個時間段太早<br />\n早到仲未識路小雨 所以佢個樣話你聽唔識佢, 而點解周杰倫可以停留係2X年前個空間係因為另一個空間(現代) 個琴已經爛左 姐係已經無得番轉頭 咁佢就永遠停留左係個個空間 而所有人都見到佢)"},{"pid":"06f29cf7767abded09ef61ee5f396ea29d90e38f","tid":136531,"uid":38599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T06:28:10.000Z","msg":"你咁講完 我覺得劇情同你的名字有d似<br />\n利申 兩套都有睇"},{"pid":"af5bb4db5c14553981fcd2e5e625d78732a6853b","tid":136531,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T06:33:03.000Z","msg":"呢套嘢係咪又係秋生做姐撚老竇？<br />\n記得秋生喺入面都幾正"},{"pid":"f86e486fc1dc295dab3ff8c72ecb5bb89c34b969","tid":136531,"uid":21501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T06:36:06.000Z","msg":"琴房果段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d473b616a3704d6bfd7a39ca2f6b58cb29da7c","tid":136531,"uid":3567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T06:38:10.000Z","msg":"呢套令到周董人氣更上一層樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bbae19aaa330520ef1fa5dd350eeeddea3f4d87","tid":136531,"uid":11581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"